title: Emon
subtitle: Developer
about: Sharing is who I am, and teaching is where I am at my best, because I've been on both sides of that equation, and getting to deliver useful training is my meaningful way to be a part of the creative community. I've spent a long time watching others learn, and teach, to refine how I work with you to be efficient, useful and, most importantly, memorable.I want you to carry what I've shown you into a bright future.
